main event: Observers watched an octagonal object with lights blinking on and off, flying close together with two other objects in New York City in 1966.
interesting points: One witness saw a plate-like flying object just over the buildings.
The descriptions are consistent with observations of an astronomical object.
The object seemed to be flying at varied speeds and elevations.
The sighting lasted for about 1 minute.
sighted object: octagonal object with blinking lights, two other flying objects
